#. Description of the plugin
#: agnosis.php
msgid ""
"Art blooming out of oblivion. Email your art, AI polishes it, the world sees "
"it. A free, federated publishing network for independent artists."
msgstr ""
"Sanaa inachanua kutoka gizani. Tuma sanaa yako kwa barua pepe, AI huipepeta "
"na kuipamba, kisha dunia huiiona. Mtandao wa uchapishaji huru na wa "
"federesheni kwa wasanii binafsi."

