#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:416
msgid ""
"Your submission has been processed. Here's what our AI curator came up with "
"— take a look and let us know if it's ready to publish."
msgstr ""
"Uwasilishaji wako umeshughulikiwa. Hii ndio AI curators wetu imekuja nayo — "
"itazame na utuambie ikiwa iko tayari kuchapishwa."

