msgid ""
"Small line identifying the artist whose subdomain is currently being viewed. "
"Renders nothing on the main Agnosis site."
msgstr ""
"Mstari mfupi unaotambulisha msanii ambaye kikoa kidogo chake kwa sasa "
"kinaonyeshwa. Huweka kitu chochote kwenye tovuti kuu ya Agnosis."

